e-mails don't come to me.

00:54:55.630 --> 00:54:59.590
I mean, even if it's addressed
to me, it goes to my assistant

00:54:59.590 --> 00:55:02.450
and they get printed out.

00:55:02.450 --> 00:55:08.950
And I get all my
emails at 11:00 AM.

00:55:08.950 --> 00:55:12.340
