in terms of any admin,

00:55:23.050 --> 00:55:25.480
it all shows up in
a folder at 11:00

00:55:25.480 --> 00:55:29.500
and by about 11:15,
11:20, I'm done.

00:55:29.500 --> 00:55:32.850
I'm done with whatever
responses, whatever--

00:55:32.850 --> 00:55:34.780
and my response usually
are chicken scratch.

00:55:34.780 --> 00:55:37.222
